## Available shadcn/ui Components

Common components available in `@/components/ui`:

- `Button` - Button component with variants
- `Card`, `CardHeader`, `CardTitle`, `CardContent`, `CardFooter` - Card components
- `Input` - Input field
- `Label` - Form label
- `Textarea` - Textarea field
- `Select` - Select dropdown
- `Checkbox` - Checkbox input
- `Separator` - Divider/separator
- `Spinner` - Loading spinner
- `Field`, `FieldLabel`, `FieldError`, `FieldDescription`, `FieldGroup` - Form field components
- `InputOTP`, `InputOTPGroup`, `InputOTPSlot` - OTP input component
- `Sonner` (toast) - Toast notifications

Import components as needed from `@/components/ui/{component-name}`.
